precis:
Amendments to the CANADA OIL AND GAS DRILLING REGULATIONS which insert
cross-references to the "Certificate of Fitness" and the "Installations"
Regulations and will require an operator to obtain a Certificate of Fitness
where the work is to be carried out in offshore areas.
